snippet.title: Mida's Adventure - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Available now on Steam!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1998420/Midas_Adventure/

Mida is an adventurer seeking after lost technological artifacts. What trouble will she face along the way? Jump back to the past in an experience influenced by Shareware games of old.

You can follow Recall Software on Twitter for more updates: 
https://twitter.com/RecallSoftware

#GameMaker #GameMakerStudio2 #Shareware
